text: Located on a spacious corner lot just inside of Division 3, you will love this setup! There's a gorgeous covered deck for outdoor enjoyment year-round. Newer stove, flooring, updated bathroom and more! Well cared for, well lit and ready for you to start making memories at the Glen at Maple Falls! Wood shed and shed on site. Community amenities include Nooksack River access, parks, trails, pools, playgrounds, disc golf & year-round events. Gated access w/ 24/7 security. Comes fully furnished & is located just 30 minutes form Bellingham & 15 minutes from the base of Mt. Baker & Silver Lake. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

Discover unparalleled waterfront living in this 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo w/ unobstructed views. The open-concept main floor is bathed in natural light, w/ expansive windows and high ceilings. Entertain on the large private patio or enjoy the beach fire pit just steps from your door. The oversized primary bedroom offers the soothing sound of waves and stunning bay and mountain views from every window. Moor your boat out back for easy crabbing trips. With 3 yr new flooring, carpet, SS appliances, a newer hot water tank, excellent established HOA with low dues, this rare gem!

This beautiful top floor unit features stainless appliances, hard surface countertops and a great open floor plan. Large common areas allow for larger group gatherings. Lots of great amenities, close to restaurants and just 5 minutes from downtown Lynden!

Welcome to this charming rambler in Glenhaven offering single-story living with 3 bedrooms and 1 bath. Set on a spacious, fully fenced double lot, this home features cozy electric heating throughout, complemented by a wood stove in the living room for added warmth. The property boasts a massive 1200 sq ft shop with 12' ceilings, fully insulated and ready for electrical installation, making it a versatile space for projects or storage. Enjoy the many amenities, including a park, a clubhouse, a pool, scenic trails, and 3 boat launches all within walking distance. Conveniently located with easy access to I-5 for effortless commuting.

Escape to your very own sanctuary in the woods, just mins away from Barkley Village & DT BHAM. This stunning home has endless features to offer. The kitchen has a huge multi level island & a walk-in pantry. Large vaulted ceilings & exposed wood beams in the living room & kitchen. Beautifully crafted trim work adds a touch of elegance throughout the home. Continue on the main floor & you'll find an office, 1/2 bath, utility room, & the primary bedroom. Primary bed boasts an amazing tiled shower. Descend the beautifully tiled stairs to the large flex space, perfect for any need. You'll also find 2 additional bedrooms, each with en suite bathrooms & walk-in closets. Oversized 3 car garage. New A/C installed just in time for the warm months.

Updated 3 bed 2.5 bath home on a quiet cul-de-sac in Tweed Twenty/Silver Beach neighborhood. This open-concept home features a spacious, beautifully renovated kitchen with new appliances, and gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the first floor. Primary bedroom on the main level. Brand new composite deck and a level and fenced backyard with raised beds. Room for RV or boat parking. Lake Whatcom is around the corner, as well as Northridge Park (trail and playground). Or, hop on the Railroad Trail to Whatcom Falls Park or even downtown. A sweet home in a magical little area of Bellingham!

INVESTOR/ FIRST TIME HOME BUYER ALERT! Perfect duplex, each with two bedrooms 1 full bath, open floor plan with kitchen, dining area, and spacious living rooms. Separate laundry room and ample closet space. Updated flooring, and fixtures. each has its own covered parking with outdoor storage and plenty more parking spots in front. Huge shared, fenced backyard with planter boxes and back alley! All this is centrally located steps from Barkley Village on a quiet street. Hurry this won't last long

Single level condo in great location, walking distance to shopping at both Whole Foods and Fred Meyer. This upgraded unit is partially handicap equipped with safety bars in the primary bathroom and ramp access through the garage. Featuring bamboo floors, french doors with blinds inside the glass leading to your deck with a view of the greenbelt, 2nd bedroom has a Murphy bed with desk, 1 year old washer/dryer, built in banquette in the dining room, and a new roof in 2017. Well run HOA with strong financials. Pets allowed with a maximum of 2 per unit. This is a gated community but NOT a 55+ property. Gated access to complex.

The Clover by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a rambler home design with all-season allure. Enter past the chic front door and find two secondary bedrooms and a Hall Bathroom. The Gourmet Kitchen features 3cm Quartz Counters, Stainless Steel appliances and a Grand Butlers Pantry. The Signature Outdoor Room is capped in Trex Composite Decking and connects the Great Room and Dining room, illuminated by a luxurious nine bulb Dining room chandelier. The Grand Suite awaits off these main living areas and features an expansive walk-in dressing room, designer free-standing tub and frameless walk-in shower. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

Come home to this private & functional property that has it all: stunning Mt. Baker views, 4.9 acres, ADU, 2 large shops, solar power and more! The 2, 507 sqft single-level home features vaulted ceilings, A/C and a front row seat to every Mt. Baker sunrise & sunset. The spacious primary bedroom with en suite features a walk-in closet, jetted tub & door to backyard. The main living area is light & bright with tall windows and skylights. ADU is form & function: 900sqft 2 bed apartment w/ large dedicated deck, 4 garage bays including a dedicated RV bay. Last but not least, a standalone 1, 000sqft shop with office and lift. Enjoy the peace and quiet of your own private 5 acre retreat at the end of a paved private road. Must see in person!

This meticulously maintained move-in ready home is what youve been waiting for! The 4 BD/2.25BA Craftsman Home offers an abundance of natural light through its windows and skylights. The open and spacious kitchen has SS appliances and plenty of storage space. Youll enjoy the coziness of the fireplace and the space with vaulted ceilings in the living room. Primary bedroom is connected to a walk-in closet and a double vanity ensuite. Park your car inside a large 2-car garage, which also has 220 power plugs and built-in storage. Access to pools, beaches, tennis courts, hiking trails, parks, playgrounds, clubhouse, are some of the wonderful amenities the Sudden Valley Community offers.

Charming Craftsman style home with ADU perched on top of Sehome Hill, backing to the Arboretum. This quaint 2 bed/1 bath home features brand new flooring on main level & recently refinished hardwood floors in bedrooms. Daylight unfinished basement plumbed for a full bath offers endless potential. Enjoy morning coffees on the front porch while taking in the beautiful view. Fully fenced private backyard leads to a spacious 550sq.ft. ADU 1bd/1bth perfect for generating additional rental income w/additional parking in back. A trail right outside your backyard takes you directly into the arboretum to campus, making this the ideal location for those who love easy access to nature & downtown Bellingham. Exterior recently painted for a fresh look.

Nestled between Lake Whatcom & the Puget Sound, w/ views over downtown Bellingham & the Bay lies this Barkley home ready for your personal touch. Fresh interior paint, new carpet, high ceilings, & refinished oak floors create a warm, inviting atmosphere. Its open layout, gas range, & large bar are perfect for hosting, while easy-care mature landscaping adds charm. With a main-floor bed & bath, it's ideal for any stage of life. Enjoy the upstairs primary bedroom's en-suite bath, walk-in closet, & cozy fireplace, ft. a west facing rooftop deck perfect for morning coffee & evening sunsets. A short walk from Barkley's shops, restaurants, & cinema, as well as Northridge Park & Bellingham trails, this home offers convenience & comfort year-round.

Charming 1910 Farmhouse on Flat, Sunny Acreage with a Huge Shop! This cozy 1, 600 sqft home features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and 2 bonus rooms, offering plenty of space for all. The expansive yard is fully fenced, complete with fruit trees and garden space - perfect for summer entertaining. A 2, 800 sqft shop provides ample room for hobbies, storage, or livestock. This 4.3 acre property with pasture space is the best of both worlds being only a bike ride away from the fabulous Birch Bay beaches, walking berm, shops and restaurants! Numerous upgrades have been made over the last three years, with room for your personal touchpriced for you to make it your own. Don't miss the chance to create your dream rural retreat!

This beautifully maintained, single-owner 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom rambler has been lovingly cared for since its construction. The open floor plan offers vaulted ceilings and hardwood floors, while the modern kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, cherry cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a double-sink vanity and walk-in shower. Enjoy the warmth of the gas fireplace or unwind in the fully fenced backyard. Additional highlights include 9' ceilings, new exterior paint (2024), and a 2-car garage with finished walls, fresh paint and trim. Near I-5, shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, walking trails and more. Move in ready!
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: 3 bed 2 1/2 bath, 2, 160 sq. feet in Spring Creek Meadows of King Mt. with fresh paint inside and outside. Wood and tile floors throughout, granite kitchen countertops, upgraded cabinets and stainless appliances. Lots of built in shelving units with ample storage throughout including the garage. Two gas fireplaces, one in the living room and one in the large primary bedroom with built in shelving and drawers. Primary bath has double sinks with solid top and walk-in shower. Built in vac system. Enjoy the trex deck in back thru the sliding or french doors with a secluded back yard that backs up to open space land. Don't miss this better than new home.
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Build your dream home on 5 acres and enjoy the privacy and peacefulness the mountains provide. This build site is ready to go! Approved 4 bedroom septic design, shared well installed with pump and underground pump house and pressure tanks, power on site complete with transformer and temp power meter approved by PSE. Current owners have a site plan approved by Whatcom County. This is an opportunity you don't want to pass up!

Nestled in a serene and private Geneva neighborhood, this home sits on an oversized, tranquil third-acre lot. Beautifully maintained for 40 plus yrs by the same family, this one-level home features a spacious, updated kitchen open to the living areas, that is perfect for entertaining. Expansive windows and sliders invite natural light and provide views of the beautifuly landscaped and very private fully fenced, flat yard that is framed by towering evergreens. Enjoy abundant storage throughout, with more in an oversized 2-car attached garage. Situated in a peaceful, ZERO-traffic location, youre just two blocks from Lake Whatcom and moments from Galbraith Mountain trails and three picturesque city parks. Two backyard sheds included.

Great price for a large lot with 80ft of frontage and backing onto acreage. Recent soils tests indicates a septic system could be approved with a curtain drain. Nice trees and close to the Bald Eagle Golf Club, beaches and parks. At this price a solid investment!!

Welcome to Whispering Meadows! This spacious 3-bedroom, 1.75-bath home boasts all the latest trendy fixtures. The main living area is highlighted by vaulted ceilings that create an open & bright atmosphere. The kitchen is a showstopper with its modern design, featuring chic pendant lighting over the island, soft-close cabinets, quartz countertops, & SS appliances. The primary bedroom offers a large walk-in closet, a double vanity, & a walk-in shower. The home also has a huge private backyard perfect for entertaining. Ductless mini-splits to keep you comfortable year-round. Plus, rest easy knowing this house is not in a flood zone. This beautifully designed rambler is exactly what you've been searching for.

This beautiful 1ac property nestled among treed & hobby farm acreage has TWO homes, fruit trees, ample yard space, a small pond & exceptional privacy. Main home built in 1968 is a 3 bed 1 bath manu home w/ a media room & large attached sunroom. 1 bed 1 bath ADU/MiL unit has its own kitchen, heating, & separate entrance W/ a covered breezeway between the homes. Mostly fenced, w/ beautiful mature trees & plenty of flat parking area. Both homes need new roofs and other repairs to bring them back to their glory days. Manu home has some mold in the bathroom, take caution when viewing. ADU is in better condition needing new roof, 1 window, some floor/ceiling repair. Cash only due to condition & age of the home. Great rental/multi-gen potential!

This Birchwood neighborhood updated classic 1960s home has it all: an extra large lot, mature landscaping, and excellent neighborhood schools. The 2100 sq ft home features 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms on a third of an acre. It has been well cared for and boasts two fireplaces, a two car garage, and natural light all day long. There have been many updates including new engineered hardwood flooring, solid wood trim and doors, a new roof, and a beautiful large deck. The all-season landscaping was thoughtfully designed for maximum outdoor living. The home is close to all that Bellingham has to offer.
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Welcome home to your endearing Silver Beach bungalow! This charming 842 sqft home is the perfect blend of cozy & cool. With 2BDS, 1BA and tall ceilings, this home is packed with delightful updates. Inside you'll find solid floors & a spacious kitchen. A full bath conveniently offers W/D & large vanity. Stay comfy year-round with a mini split heat pump + AC & enjoy the perks of a rewired home & recent electrical panel upgrade. Kick back on the deck in the newly fenced yard & take in the partial yet stunning lake views or tend a flourishing & sunny garden. Newer roof ~2019 + solar panels. Nature lovers will appreciate nearby trails or a dip in Lake Whatcom. Carport w/ extra parking + shop space. Just steps to the new coffee shop Lakeline!

Discover the epitome of tranquil living at 719 Peace Arch Ct in Blaine! Nestled near downtown Blaine, this cozy rambler offers seamless access to I-5 and the Canadian border for your convenience. Step into your own slice of paradise with a lush greenhouse, inviting hot tub, and a built-in gas BBQ perfect for entertaining. Ample space for all your vehicles with dedicated RV parking. Inside, a sleek kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances awaits. This 3-bed, 1.5-bath haven exudes warmth and charm, making it the ideal retreat to call home. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity.

This spacious 4, 276 square foot custom home is situated in the desirable Silver Beach neighborhood. The main floor features a primary bedroom with spacious ensuite, great room with walls of glass, towering ceilings that open to the dining room adjacent to a large corner kitchen & a massive full length deck. The upper floor includes 2 bedrooms, large bonus room, and a full bath. The lower level has a mother in law suite with nearly 1, 500 square feet with separate entrance featuring a family room, kitchen, 2 bedrooms, full bath, and large covered patio. The private backyard is fully fenced with a covered patio. All this & more, yet only minutes from Barkley Village which offers restaurants, theaters, coffee shops and tons of walking trails.

Discover charm and comfort in this inviting home on Eldridge Avenue, nestled in Bellingham's sought-after Columbia neighborhood. Fresh interior paint highlights the cozy ambiance, complemented by main floor oak wood floors and a warming Wood fireplace. Enjoy bay views from the upper-level bedroom with new carpet, and a well-appointed kitchen featuring newer stainless steel appliances, an oversized refrigerator, & convenient breakfast nook. Step outside to a fully fenced private backyard with a spacious covered deck and inviting patio. The lower level offers versatile flex space with built-ins, perfect for displaying your treasures and additional storage spaces. This home also includes a one-car garage and is located close to all amenities.
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Welcome to this inviting 4-bed, 3-bath rambler on the fringe of the Columbia neighborhood! Built on a readily subdividable multi-family zoned lot (buyer to verify), this property offers investment opportunity, future expansion or simply enjoying the extra space. Step inside to discover a well-maintained, spacious interior with bright, open living spaces, ample sunlight & a new back deck perfect for entertaining. The fully fenced yard includes generous space to garden, while the detached garage/shop offers versatile storage. The covered RV/boat parking is an added bonus. With Squalicum Creek Park nearby, outdoor enthusiasts will relish easy access to scenic trails. Dont miss out on this charming home in a prime location in Bellingham.

text: This 2, 312 sqft Custom Rubicon Home offers 3 bedrooms & 2.5 baths with a luxurious primary suite on the main floor featuring a spacious ensuite with solid surface quartz showers & countertops. The expansive kitchen boasts quartz countertops, while the living area impresses with soaring 12-ft ceilings that step through to a private covered outdoor living space, complete with built-in Blaze BBQ and beverage fridge. Perfect for entertaining! High-end finishes are found throughout, ideally located near Galbraith Mountain, Whatcom Falls Park, and Lake Whatcom, with easy access to local shops. Enjoy a fully fenced backyard with double gates for RV or boat parking, plus a low-maintenance yard. Welcome home!

Welcome to this immaculately renovated 3 bed, 2.5 bath home nestled in the Birch Bay Village community. The meticulously updated kitchen features updated cabinetry, solid surface countertops and high end appliances. The inviting open concept main floor seamlessly integrates indoor and outdoor living, leading to the large Trex deck that overlooks the private yard and surrounding greenbelt/pond. The stunning gas fireplace and new mini splits offer efficient heating and cooling for year round comfort. BBV offers an impressive array of amenities, including 24/7 security, golf course, pool, pickle ball, tennis, boat moorage and marina access. Don't miss your chance to make this house your home and enjoy the beautiful PNW beach life.

Explore the under-construction Cypress model in Woodberry at Semiahmoo, featuring a rare 3-car garage and customizable upgrades. This spacious home spans 2690 sf and offers main-level living with a Primary suite, office, dining room, and open kitchen-living area, plus 1.5 baths. Upstairs, discover 2 bedrooms, a bath, and a loft area. Enjoy high-quality finishes such as quartz countertops, soft-close cabinets, stainless appliances, mini-split heating, and a durable limited lifetime roof. Outdoor living is complemented by a patio. Just 25 minutes from Costco and 10 minutes from the border, the community boasts amenities like a golf club, marina, waterfront park, spa, tennis club, and trails for kayaking and biking.
